Version 0.4.8.2016 (July 20, 2017 bugfix update)

Installation:  see INSTALL
User's manual: see html-doc/manual.html
Updates:       see http://xournal.sourceforge.net/

See also: http://sourceforge.net/projects/xournal

# Change on this branch

I find the default accelerators to be very hard to use/reach on the keyboard so
I did a few changes.

Accelerators change on this branch:

- Tools
  - Esc - Hand
  - F1 - Pencil
  - F2 - Ruler
  - F3 - Select rectangle
  - F4 - Vertical space
  - F5 - Zoom out
  - F6 - Zoom in
  - F7 - Highlighter
- Colors
  - Ctrl-1 - Black
  - Ctrl-2 - Blue
  - Ctrl-3 - Red
  - Ctrl-4 - Green
  - Ctrl-5 - Orange

I also find very handy to set `Region select` to pen button 2 in the menus.

To build the package for archlinux:
- clone this repo
- Build with: makepkg --noextract -f
- Install with: sudo pacman -U xournal-0.4.8.2016-1-x86_64.pkg.tar.xz